title: Frogs Data
description:
Description
The frogs data frame has 212 rows and 11 columns.
The data are on the distribution of the Southern Corroboree
frog, which occurs in the Snowy Mountains area of New South Wales,
Australia.

parameters.pres.abs: 0 = frogs were absent, 1 = frogs were present
parameters.distance: distance in meters to nearest extant population
